Are you hungry?

32
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,900
Not really.

33
00:03:08,770 --> 00:03:11,990
What? Do you have something to tell me?

34
00:03:12,770 --> 00:03:14,550
Yeah.

35
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:21,460
Quickly, go to bed.

36
00:03:23,210 --> 00:03:25,570
<i>I want to tell you...</i>

37
